<h3>Sequence Diagram</h3>

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller
    participant getBranchesForSession
    participant globalStateCache as globalState Cache
    participant remoteBranchesCache as in-memory Cache
    participant apiClient

    Caller->>getBranchesForSession: call(forceRefresh?)
    alt forceRefresh=false AND globalState cache valid
        getBranchesForSession->>globalStateCache: get(cacheKey)
        globalStateCache-->>getBranchesForSession: cached BranchesCache
        getBranchesForSession-->>Caller: return cached data (early exit)
    else cache miss or forceRefresh=true
        getBranchesForSession->>remoteBranchesCache: get(sourceName)
        alt in-memory cache hit AND not stale AND not forceRefresh
            remoteBranchesCache-->>getBranchesForSession: cachedData (branches, defaultBranch)
        else in-memory cache miss or stale or forceRefresh
            getBranchesForSession->>apiClient: getSource(sourceName)
            alt API success
                apiClient-->>getBranchesForSession: sourceDetail
                getBranchesForSession->>remoteBranchesCache: set(sourceName, cachedData)
            else API failure
                apiClient-->>getBranchesForSession: throw Error
                Note over getBranchesForSession: ⚠️ 古いキャッシュがあっても<br/>branches=[defaultBranch] のみ返却
            end
        end
        getBranchesForSession->>globalStateCache: update(cacheKey, newCache)
        getBranchesForSession-->>Caller: return branches result
    end
```

